Package: leachatetools
Title: Water Quality Analysis Tools for Leachate-Impacted Waters
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Robin", "Shannon", email = "rjs@robinshannon.net",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for analysing water quality in systems potentially impacted
    by landfill leachate. Core capabilities: species sensitivity distribution
    (SSD) based potentially affected fraction (PAF) calculations using
    ANZECC/ANZG toxicity data; multi-substance PAF (msPAF / AmsPAF) with
    local background adjustment via the Added Risk Approach; and end-member
    mixing analysis for leachate detection (LMF).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
